# Build context for the Arcane Cloud image (repo-root context). Keep it lean and never bake secrets
# or host-built artifacts into the image.
**/node_modules
.git
.gitignore
**/dist
**/.next
**/.turbo
**/.arcane
# The cloud image does not need the web apps (heaviest deps) — trim them from the context.
apps/landing
apps/dashboard
# Secrets are provided at runtime via `fly secrets`, never copied in.
**/.env
**/.env.*
!**/.env.example
# Misc
bun.lockb
*.log
.DS_Store
docs
